Rating: 3
Loved taste of this lasagne. Only change I made was to microwave the butternut squash for about two or three minutes and then cut it open and scooped out squash. Otherwise, butternut squash is too hard to peel and cut. Obviously, it cut down on prep time and I don't think if effected the taste.

Rating: 4
Wonderful dish. I am not a fan of meatless lasagne, but this dish is amazing. Perfect blending of flavors. I added an additional teaspoon of sage to the filling to enhance the flavor of the squash. Don't skimp on the mozzarella, be sure to use fresh cheese. The filling took me about 25 minutes to thicken to the proper consistancy (not the 10 the recipe says). Would definitely make this dish again and again, it's a new favorite.